Summary: I videoed a UFO by accident when videoing jets taking off at SF airport
divs: Sighting DetailsI didn't see this UFO with my eyes,my Canon 5D Mark ii saw it and taped it when I was shooting video at San Francisco International Airport.I only saw it after I was editing the video.There are 2 commercial Jets in the video for reference.The object enters San Francisco Airspace at a high rate of speed,so fast that the human eye wouldn't be able to see this.It "skips" through the airspace with what looks like a couple of quick directional changes,kind of a zigzag.It did "flash" a very bright white strobe twice in the footage.
trends: There have been 127 other sightings in San Francisco
There were no other sightings in San Francisco on or around August 29th 2012
